description: You can use this skill to get the current donation total for Zeldathon, a charity gaming marathon that has raised over one million dollars for various charities. This skill is not officially endorsed by Zeldathon.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask Zelda Total for the donation total
Alexa, ask Zelda Total to give me the donation total
Alexa, ask Zelda Total for how much has zeldathon raised
name: Unofficial Zeldathon Total
shortDescription: Get the donation total for Zeldathon, a charity gaming marathon!
